@startuml
title Input - Level 1

skinparam ParticipantPadding 8

actor "Player / user" as User
participant "Operating system" as OS
participant "Sparkle" as Sparkle
participant "Widget" as Widget

User -> OS : moves mouse or presses key
OS -> Sparkle : sends input message
Sparkle -> Widget : calls the matching event method

alt widget handles it
	Widget --> Sparkle : event consumed
else widget ignores it
	Widget --> Sparkle : event continues
end

note over Sparkle,Widget
Sparkle turns platform messages into easier
C++ events that widgets can react to.
end note

@enduml
